Subject: [PATCH] units: systemd-hostnamed: Remove Private network option

Avoid issue when booting on our platforms

Signed-off-by: Baptiste Chauloux <baptiste.chauloux@st.com>
---
 units/systemd-hostnamed.service.in | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/units/systemd-hostnamed.service.in b/units/systemd-hostnamed.service.in
index d29e9ff..a454b92 100644
--- a/units/systemd-hostnamed.service.in
+++ b/units/systemd-hostnamed.service.in
@@ -17,7 +17,6 @@ WatchdogSec=3min
 CapabilityBoundingSet=CAP_SYS_ADMIN
 PrivateTmp=yes
 PrivateDevices=yes
-PrivateNetwork=yes
 ProtectSystem=strict
 ProtectHome=yes
 ProtectControlGroups=yes
